Double Punch/Manterror/Injector/Stinkbomb/Ramhorn:

::Double Punch heard a crunch, spinning around he spots Quickstrike::
"Well, well."
::Raising a pincher, Double Punch fires a single energy signature seeking 
missile at Quickstrike's torso::

=========

::Manterror stopped as he reached Hell Beast::
"What are your or...orders sir?" (the paused by noticing half o Hell Beast's 
face was missing)

::Injector stopped behind Manterror:
"Yeah, Hell Beast, what do you want us to do?"

============

::Stinkbomb slowly got up, the pain passing for the most part::
"Th...that stinking mantis...when I get my hands on him..."

"Don't bother, Stinkbomb.  We have to stop the Predacons."
::Ramhorn slowly got up, dents in his armor::  


::Both of them charge out o the engine room::
